{
  "stem": "7273.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we actually, then she said, look, in, Chrzanow, where I was in the ghetto, there are some nice Polish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so she wanted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we took the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the train took us over Auschwitz to Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for the first time, I saw this special line which went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not to make.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And each station had, like, station police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I thought, my God, we must look a bit wild.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to the station police, and I started to-- to ask about when the next train comes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I kept him in conversation, that he wouldn't get the idea, you know, to ask for paper, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I succeeded with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we-- we came to Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to know us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Katowice I have someone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we took from Chrzanow, again, we went back to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And where she said, look I am the Aryan of us both.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll go and buy the tickets, and you sit down in the waiting room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was sitting in the waiting room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sitting, sitting, and I thought, my God, that is a long time she doesn't come back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all stations have these [INAUDIBLE] polizei-- that means they check for papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Like in the restaurant I was sitting, they come in and ask everybody for papers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I thought that is my end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So as they came once, I-- I went the other side out, so that I avoided them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I thought, I have to look at the counter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At the ticket counter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Where is she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were two German civilians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They looked like civilians, but they were these criminal polizei.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
